ku''|\u767d\u9280\u30b8\u30e3\u30c3\u30af|}}, 2010 (''Silver Hijack'')\n*{{nihongo|''Masukar\u0113do Hoteru (Masquerade Hotel)''|\u30de\u30b9\u30ab\u30ec\u30fc\u30c9\u30fb\u30db\u30c6\u30eb|}}, 2011\n*{{nihongo|''[[Namiya Zakkaten no Kiseki]]''|\u30ca\u30df\u30e4\u96d1\u8ca8\u5e97\u306e\u5947\u8e5f|}}, 2012 (''Miracles of the Namiya General Store'')\n*{{nihongo|''Mugen-bana''|\u5922\u5e7b\u82b1|}}, 2013 (''Dream Flower'')\n*{{nihongo|''Utsuro na yujika''|\u865a\u308d\u306a\u5341\u5b57\u67b6|}}, 2014 (''Hollow Cross'')\n*{{nihongo|''Ningyo no Nemuru Ie''|\u4eba\u9b5a\u306e\u7720\u308b\u5bb6|}}, 2015 (''The House Where the Mermaid Sleeps'')\n*{{nihongo|''[[Laplace's Witch (novel)|Rapurasu no Majo]]''|\u30e9\u30d7\u30e9\u30b9\u306e\u9b54\u5973|}}, 2015 (''Laplace's Witch)''\n*{{nihongo|''Kiken'na b\u012bnasu''|\u5371\u967a\u306a\u30d3\u30fc\u30ca\u30b9|}}, 2016 (''Dangerous Venus)''\n*{{nihongo|''Kib\u014d no ito''|\u5e0c\u671b\u306e\u7cf8 |}}, 2019 (''Thread of hope)''\n\n===Essay collections===\n*{{nihongo|''Anogoro Bokuraha Ahodeshita''|\u3042\u306e\u9803\u50d5\u3089\u306f\u30a2\u30db\u3067\u3057\u305f |}}, 1995 (''When We Were Stupid'')\n*{{nihongo|''Charenji?''|\u3061\u3083\u308c\u3093\u3058?|}}, 2004 (''Challenge?'')\n*{{nihongo|''Sai Ensu?''|\u3055\u3044\u3048\u3093\u3059?|}}, 2005 (''Science?'')\n*{{nihongo|''Yume wa Torino o Kakemeguru''|\u5922\u306f\u30c8\u30ea\u30ce\u3092\u304b\u3051\u3081\u3050\u308b|}}, 2006 (''Dreams over Turin'')\n*{{nihongo|''Tabun Saigo no o Aisatsu''|\u305f\u3076\u3093\u6700\u5f8c\u306e\u5fa1\u6328\u62f6|}}, 2007 (''Probably the Last Greeting'')\n\n===Other short story collections===\n*{{nihongo|''Tantei Kurabu''|\u63a2\u5075\u5036\u697d\u90e8|}}, 1990 (''Detective Club'')\n*{{nihongo|''Hannin no Inai Satsujin no Yoru''|\u72af\u4eba\u306e\u3044\u306a\u3044\u6bba\u4eba\u306e\u591c|}}, 1990 (''A Night of Murder with no Murderer'')\n*{{nihongo|''K\u014dts\u016b Keisatsu no Yoru''|\u4ea4\u901a\u8b66\u5bdf\u306e\u591c|}}, 1991 (''A Night o